%%
%%	Brief Manual
%%	------------
%%	Normally, Tab moves the cursor to the next tab stop on the current line.
%%	Back Tab moves the cursor to the previoys tab stop,	or to the beginning
%%	of the line.
%%
%%	A block is marked...
